title: Glary Utilities Pro 5.38.0.58 Multilingual (Portable)
description:
*****************************************************
Glary Utilities Pro 5.38.0.58 Multilingual (Portable)
*****************************************************

Release date: 09/11/2015

About v5.38: for some reason this release is not mentioned on author's webiste so far

Glary Utilities Pro 5 provides a one-stop solution for PC performance optimization

- The portable version is registered and allows running all tweaks included in the install version
- Disabled features: Context menus, AutoUpdate, CheckUpdate, SoftwareUpdate
- Unavailable features: Automation
- Usage: unzip and run Integrator_Portable, disallow internet access

Homepage http://www.glarysoft.com/glary-utilities-pro/
